<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Course Overview - SKEC</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

:root {
--bg-black: #05070a;
--teal-glow: #14b8a6;
--teal-bright: #2dd4bf;
--white: #f4faf9;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
min-height: 100vh;
background:
radial-gradient(circle at 90% 10%, rgba(20,184,166,0.55) 0%, rgba(20,184,166,0.15) 30%, transparent 55%),
radial-gradient(circle at 0% 90%, rgba(88,28,135,0.35) 0%, transparent 45%),
var(--bg-black);
font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
padding: 40px 24px;
}

.header {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 16px;
margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.back-btn {
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.15);
border: 1px solid rgba(45,212,191,0.4);
color: var(--teal-bright);
padding: 10px 16px;
border-radius: 8px;
cursor: pointer;
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 600;
transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.back-btn:hover {
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.25);
border-color: var(--teal-bright);
}

h1 {
font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
font-weight: 800;
font-size: 48px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
color: var(--teal-bright);
text-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(45,212,191,0.4);
}

.modules-grid {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
gap: 24px;
max-width: 1200px;
margin: 0 auto;
}

.module-card {
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.06);
border: 1.5px solid rgba(45,212,191,0.4);
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 28px;
cursor: pointer;
transition: transform 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
}

.module-card:hover {
transform: translateY(-6px);
background: rgba(20,184,166,0.12);
border-color: var(--teal-bright);
}

.module-card h2 {
font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
font-weight: 700;
font-size: 18px;
color: var(--teal-bright);
margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.module-card p {
font-weight: 400;
font-size: 14px;
color: rgba(244,250,249,0.75);
line-height: 1.5;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
<button class="back-btn" onclick="window.location.href='index.html'">← Back</button>
<h1>Course Overview</h1>
</div>

<div class="modules-grid">
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-1.html'">
<h2>Module 1</h2>
<p>Teacher Standards and Reflections</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-2.html'">
<h2>Module 2</h2>
<p>Narrative Writing</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-3.html'">
<h2>Module 3</h2>
<p>Persuasive Writing</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-4.html'">
<h2>Module 4</h2>
<p>Analytical Writing</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-5.html'">
<h2>Module 5</h2>
<p>Literature and Unseen Poetry</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-6.html'">
<h2>Module 6</h2>
<p>Macbeth and Romeo and Juliet</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-7.html'">
<h2>Module 7</h2>
<p>A Christmas Carol and Jekyll and Hyde</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-8.html'">
<h2>Module 8</h2>
<p>An Inspector Calls and Animal Farm</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-9.html'">
<h2>Module 9</h2>
<p>How to Improve Pupil Writing</p>
</div>
<div class="module-card" onclick="window.location.href='module-10.html'">
<h2>Module 10</h2>
<p>Behaviour for Learning</p>
</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
